Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:11.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジら４５組が\N全てを賭けて挑んだ大勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:11.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and the 45s risk it all on this bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:16.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The foreman Ohtsuki uses the 4-5-6 dice for his third roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:17.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長大槻　シゴロ賽を\N選択しての３投目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:20.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:18.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ！\N何をする！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:22.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こら！まだ回ってんじゃねえか！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:27.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're still rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:31.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,500)\pos(640,505)}Karmic Punishment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:30.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん\Nカイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:30.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:33.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こら こいつ！返せ こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:33.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give those back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:37.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくらいい目が出そうだからって\Nなんて無法だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:37.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're just breaking the rules because you could tell I rolled well!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:41.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だ… 黙れ！\Nうおっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:42.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gotta fight fire with fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:44.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無法には無法だ！\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:46.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな　聞け！こいつらは…\Nまずい！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:45.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:45.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh crap! They—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:46.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:48.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ… バカ野郎！\Nクソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:48.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:50.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃべらせるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:50.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！アタタタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:01.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:04.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞け　こいつらは\Nイカサマをした！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:04.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:08.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何を言うか！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:07.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:11.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ち 違う！違う 違う 違う！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No! No no no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:15.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違わない ここに証拠を握り込んだ\Nイカサマサイコロ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:14.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes! I have the proof in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:16.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These are loaded dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:18.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.15,0:01:17.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:20.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give those back, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,返せ！このガキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:24.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You keep making shit up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:24.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次から次へと\N根も葉もないことを…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:29.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許さん　許さんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:33.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ 大槻\Nえっ？あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:31.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Back of, Ohtsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちが改めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:35.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:39.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Odagiri, foreman of team C, speaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:39.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,申し出たのはＣ班の班長 小田切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:42.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっいや… ここはわしらが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:42.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously, we're fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:45.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,またまた　それじゃ\N意味がないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:45.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's pointless for you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:49.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見れくれ　これが奴らの\N常勝の秘密だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:49.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look! This is why they win so often!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… ま 待て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:51.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:56.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！ま 待ってくれ！それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:55.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold it! That's—!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:59.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His false luck is revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:59.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらされる偽りの強運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:01.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:01.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのからくりが白日の下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:04.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The trick is thrust into the light of day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ… 何だ？こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are these!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？どうした？おい\N何だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:17.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These dice only have sides with fours, fives, and sixes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:17.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このサイコロ\N目が４と５と６だけじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:21.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつら こんなものを？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's what he's been using!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひでえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What a dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How long have you been using these?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつから使ってたんだ？これ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:38.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,も… もちろん さっきが初めてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:38.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That was the first time, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:42.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't even plan on using them today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:42.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっいや… 今日だって\N使うつもりはなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:45.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってやがる！\N実際 使ってるじゃねえか！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the fuck are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:46.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You went and used 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだそうだ　とぼけんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:48.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:51.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいやいや　これは\N後で余興でやろうと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:53.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, really! I was gonna show 'em off later, but I accidentally rolled with the wrong set!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが交ざってしまって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけんな！\N誰がそんな話 信じる！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:57.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bullshit! No one's gonna buy that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:02.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや その証拠に２投目までは\Nこのサイコロを使わなかっただろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:01.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I didn't use them for my first two rolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:06.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このサイコロはな\Nションベンさえしなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:08.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,See, these dice are sure to roll something unless you roll a pisser!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:09.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず目が出る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最低でも４の目がな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They can't roll worse than a 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり さっきの１ ２投目は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:18.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So obviously I was using normal dice for my first two rolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通のサイコロを\N使ってたってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:26.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What if I had rolled something crappy my first time? See, I can't be cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:21.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことをして\Nもし１投目に弱い目が出たら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:23.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イカサマサイコロを\N持ってる意味なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ないじゃないか な？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:30.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使うなら１投目だ\Nうっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I was gonna use them, I'd have started with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:35.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,See, that proves I wasn't using loaded dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:36.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これこそ わしがｲｶｻﾏｻｲｺﾛを\N使ってないという証拠だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:42.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は？\Nさっきの勝負は特別だったのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:42.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That last round was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:48.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sure, if you were planning to win with the 4-5-6 dice, you'd have used them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:47.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにシゴロ賽で\N勝とうと思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:49.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使うのは１投目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:54.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Up until now, you always have when push came to shove.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までのあんたは\Nこの基本どおり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:54.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大勝負では こいつを使ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:55.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now you're just making shit up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言いがかりだ\Nいいや
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:56.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:04:02.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も この三好メモを見るまでは\N気づかなかったんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:00.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I never realized until I read Miyoshi's notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:07.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた多すぎた\N１投目に強い目が出る割合が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:06.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but you win on the first roll way too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Way too often for it to be by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶然の域をはるかに超えている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:17.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a moron for not seeing it, but it's just part of what makes the 4-5-6 dice so terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気づかなかった俺も間抜けだが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:17.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつは このシゴロ賽の持つ\Nタチの悪さみたいなもんでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:21.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロ賽は必ずしも\Nシゴロが出るわけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:21.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The 4-5-6 dice do not always roll a 4-5-6!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４の目 ５の目もある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They can roll a 4 or a 5 too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その場合 相手が勝つこともある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:29.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then the other player can win! So in a way, they're the perfect cheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これがある意味 絶妙の煙幕となり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:32.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このシゴロ賽の存在を\N隠したのである
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:32.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The existence of the 4-5-6 dice was concealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事実 俺もしょっぱなの勝負じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:39.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even I won against their 4 twice in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:39.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この賽で出た４の目に対して\N５の目で２連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大喜びしたってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed it plenty then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:46.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが記録ってのは\N冷静で客観的なもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:46.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But the records speak for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:49.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このメモで あんたのイカサマに\N気づいた俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:51.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When I realized you were cheating by reading these notes, I planned a showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:53.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつらと大勝負を仕掛けた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:57.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に２万という大金を張って\Nそっちの出方を見たが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:57.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,First, I'd bet 20 thou, and see what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:05:02.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１番手の石和が能天気に\Nイカサマサイコロを使ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Isawa rolled first, and went straight for the loaded dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:06.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は内心 ほくそえんで\Nあんたの親番を待ち
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:06.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I grinned on the inside, waiting for your turn to deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなを呼んで大勝負に出た
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then I called everyone in and bet the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:14.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But the size of the bet told you something was up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが金額のデカさが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたの猜疑心を\N揺り起こしちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You realized we were on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:17.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イカサマが\Nバレてるんじゃないかってな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからあんた この土壇場で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:22.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why you couldn't decide whether to use your loaded dice or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:23.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロ賽を使うことを\N思いとどまった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:26.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How could you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:26.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして思いとどまったって\N分かったんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通 チンチロってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:33.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally in chinchiro, once you roll, everyone's focused on the bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サイコロを\Nどんぶりに投げ入れたら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:34.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰だって どんぶりの中に\N集中するはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But during your first roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:39.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが１投目 あんた俺の目を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You were looking straight into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！\N俺がイカサマに気づいてるか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:48.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Trying to see if I knew you were cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:51.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かめにきたんだ\Nフッ 助かったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:52.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky. If you hadn't been looking at me like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:53.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの目がなきゃ\N俺は普通のサイコロを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:58.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'd have thought they were the loaded dice and made a grab.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イカサマサイコロと思い込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:58.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とんだ お手つきをしてたところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:03.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The second roll was the same, so I stayed still.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:00.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして２投目も同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:03.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃ手も足も出ない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:12.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But with that much on the line, you couldn't just leave it up to luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:06.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが ほぼ勝ちを拾えるシゴロ賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:10.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大金を前にして できることなら\N運否天賦に任せず
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつを使って勝ちたい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:15.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That was your fatal mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのスケベ心が命取りになった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:18.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたは１ ２投目の俺や\N三好たちの反応を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:21.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You watched me and Miyoshi during your first two rolls and decided we weren't on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:21.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イカサマに気づかれてないと\N判断した
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:23.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロ賽を使わないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:26.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No one seemed surprised that you weren't using the 4-5-6 dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:26.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も不思議がって\Nいなかったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:30.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だ　こいつらには\Nイカサマの仕組みに関しては
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:32.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course not. I said nothing to them about your trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も話してなかったんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:36.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\Nそれも俺の戦略
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That was part of my plan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:38.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And you walked right into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたは まんまと乗ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:42.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,On the third roll, you didn't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:41.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３投目 もう俺に目もくれなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:47.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたは故意に\Nこのサイコロを使ったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:48.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You were using these dice to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つためにな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:52.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う　違うんだよ カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… こいつ気づいてやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn it, he noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に故意じゃなかったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It wasn't on purpose at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everything! He noticed everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何もかも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:03.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事故なんだ\Nまだすっとぼけんのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It was accidental!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't keep giving us that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ\Nバカ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:04.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:08.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really! Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じてくれ　このとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:11.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけんな！\Nお前はイカサマをしたんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:08.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're a dirty cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:14.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ そうだ！\N金返せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:12.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give the money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:19.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Crap! How can I turn this around!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:19.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… マズい　どうすれば\Nわしの立場は逆転できる？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:22.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままイカサマを認めれば\Nどんな目に遭うか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:22.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to me if I admit I was cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:25.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the worst moment of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:27.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が生涯 最大の苦境！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:30.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's all that kid's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:30.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,元はといえば あのガキのせい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:33.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But he's not just some kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:34.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが あいつは単なるガキじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:38.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今にして思えば\Nあの露骨なまでの反抗も
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:42.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thinking of it, even that blatant disrespect was just to make me angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:43.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの敵がい心をあおるための\N計算ずくの行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:45.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まんまと踊らされていた…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:45.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He took me in completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イカサマ野郎！\N金返せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:48.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pay us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:52.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズが！\N単に金が欲しいだけなら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:55.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If this was just about about money, I might not have used them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしもシゴロ賽を\N使わなかったかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:59.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが あのガキに対する憎悪が
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:08:01.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But my anger pushed me into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:02.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの背中を押した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:07.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の最後に使ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:07.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In the end, I used them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:17.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんたる不覚！\N不覚！不覚！不覚！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:14.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An error! A misjudgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしカイジ君\Nあんた大したもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:21.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:24.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとだよな\Nまだサイコロが回ってる時に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:27.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm amazed you went for the bowl while the dice were still rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんぶりに手を入れるから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:30.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 最初は\N何事かと思ったけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:30.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I couldn't figure out what you were up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:36.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！\Nひらめく！大槻の脳裏に突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A flash of inspiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:37.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ohtsuki's mind races!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:41.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打ち立てる 己の議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An insight comes to him, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:45.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His logic! His argument! His justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:46.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正論　正しさ　身勝手な正義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:49.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ね！\N死んで詫びろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金返せ！\Nクズ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pay us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dickwad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,振ってない…\Nはっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？何だって？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:02.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふ… 振ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:08.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく考えると わしは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:11.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking, and I realized. I didn't really roll with the 4-5-6 dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:12.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロ賽を振ってない…\N振ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:12.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:24.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't roll the 4-5-6 dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:24.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしはシゴロ賽を振ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:30.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji grabbed the bowl before the dice settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君がどんぶりを取った\Nあの時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:30.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サイコロは まだ回っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The roll wasn't complete yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:32.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目はまだ出ていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:37.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり この勝負は未確定！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:36.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So we're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're not finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:39.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,成立してない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:42.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I haven't technically cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:42.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからイカサマもクソもない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:45.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That doesn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:46.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不成立！ノーカウント！\Nノーカウント！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:58.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't count! It doesn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノーカウントなんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:52.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノーカン！ノーカン！\Nノーカン！ノーカン！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノーカン！ノーカン！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノーカン！ノーカン！ノーカン…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:02.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Doesn't count doesn't count doesn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:04.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい！ノーカン…\N何だと！こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけんな！\N適当なこと言うな！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:06.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuck that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:07.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:09.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イカサマ野郎！\Nノーカウント…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:08.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:12.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目が出てなきゃノーカウントだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't count until the dice come up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:16.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジで言うか？\Nこの野郎 ぶっ殺…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:16.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's ki—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:19.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:22.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:26.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He may be reaching, but he's getting somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:27.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦し紛れの言い訳にしちゃ\N痛いところ突いてるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:31.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まんざら理がないわけでもない\N何言ってんだよ！カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:31.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What, Kaiji!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:34.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや さすがにカイジ君は聡明だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:34.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I knew you were clever, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目が出てなけりゃ\Nサイコロは未使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Until the dice stop, a roll isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right? It doesn't count!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な？ノーカウントだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:41.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can do it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は やり直し\N普通のサイコロで改めてやり直し
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Try again with normal—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:45.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねえ\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:44.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cut the shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:48.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A do-over? I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やり直しなんてのは\Nごめんこうむる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:51.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが\Nだ… だが？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:54.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I could keep going, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:55.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続行っていうなら考えてもいいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:05.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続行？\Nそうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:11.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You and your buddies have been winning sharing those dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:08.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らは ここまで仲間うちだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:11.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな特殊な賽を回して\N勝ち続けてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:16.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや… だからそれは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:16.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:20.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ あえて そのルールで\N続行といこうじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:20.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll play by those rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:23.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\Nただし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:27.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But you get the lowest roll these 4-5-6 dice can make.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:27.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたの目は\Nこのシゴロ賽における最低の目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:30.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４だ\N４？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:29.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:32.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you expect even less of a penalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:32.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このくらいのペナルティは\N当然だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:36.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ…\Nそして その４の目に対して
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:41.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And all six of us are going to roll with loaded dice against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:41.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち６人 同じく\N特殊なサイを使って勝負する
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:44.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:47.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:57.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカめ　やった！やったやった！\Nノーカウントが生きた！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:57.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I did it! He let it pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:01.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I though if I got caught I'd have to pay double, triple,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:12:00.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなイカサマがバレたら\N普通は張った額の２倍か３倍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:04.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　過去にさかのぼっての\N弁済も考えられた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:05.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,no, pay everything back! But instead we continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを続行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:15.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if all six roll a 4-5-6, at double 507,000 the most I'll pay is just over a million!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:10.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に奴ら６人全員が\Nシゴロを出しても
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:15.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,50万7000の倍\N100万ちょいの負けで決着がつく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:19.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All I need to do is make it through this, and then act contrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここを切り抜ければ あとは\Nうやむやにしちまえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:30.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:30.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残った 生き残った\N生き残った！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:33.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:33.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残った！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:39.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お人よしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:38.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What a pushover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負が無効になって\N全部 無駄になることを恐れおって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd lose everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:48.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… やっぱバカじゃん\Nハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:47.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He must be retarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:53.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押し返した\Nゴネ得 ゴネ得 ゴネ得！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:52.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I turned it around, just by complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So how about it? We gonna do this or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:57.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい どうなんだ？\N受けるのか？受けないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:01.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,く… 苦しい条件だが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're killing me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:05.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方あるまい\Nおお！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジはまず この１番手\N沼川に振らせる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:14.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,First, Kaiji has Numakawa, the first player, roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His roll is a 4! A draw with Ohtsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:23.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出目は４　大槻と引き分ける
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:24.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 確認する
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's make this perfectly clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:33.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,As a dealer, you rolled a 4. Now all of us are rolling against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親の１回目　あんたの目は４
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:33.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを受けて俺たちが振る
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,None of us are using normal dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その賽は通常の賽じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前もって用意した特殊な賽だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:38.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're using specially-prepared dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:44.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just like your side, we're sharing our dice between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:42.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その特殊賽を\Nあんたらがそうしたように
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちも仲間うちで回して使う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:47.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No problems, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:49.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,構わないんだな？それで\Nうう…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウザいな もう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dude, whatever, just roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいからさっさと\N振れっちゅうんじゃい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:58.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'm getting sick of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わ… 分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:59.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい加減 演技も疲れるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then let's get this started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:02.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃ始めるか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:13.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？\N三好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:11.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:15.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと割に合わないって\N思ったろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This ain't good enough, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:18.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…\Nここで６人が勝負したとして
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we all take him on with these,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:21.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,we walk out of here with maybe an extra five hundred thou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:21.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入ってくるのはプラス50万
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:24.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we're really lucky, eight hundred or a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:24.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　80万か100万
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Could be one, could be the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは分からないが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:30.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but it's not enough of a reward for blowing the doors off his trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:31.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれだけのイカサマを\N暴いた割には その程度かって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… まあ確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ　安心しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:36.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:40.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,済ますわけねえだろ\Nそんなもんで！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll have to pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A lot more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:52.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念力が賽の目を\N左右するんだったな？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:52.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Karma is guiding these dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Suck on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:56.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食らえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:04.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is karmic punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:04.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,因果応報　天誅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:08.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is what you get for cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:07.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これがお前のイカサマの報いだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:14.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He rolls snake eyes! They pay five times!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目はピンゾロ　５倍づけ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:19.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are these dice!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何じゃ このサイコロ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:23.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１！１！１！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:23.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One, one, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:27.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing but ones on each side! One one one one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６面全部ピンじゃねえか！\Nピン ピン ピン！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:30.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These are our dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちはこっちで\N用意させてもらった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカもん！通るか こんなもん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:33.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bullshit! I'm not gonna—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:38.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念押ししたはずだ\Nお前たちと同じように
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:41.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember? We agreed that we'd each use our own special dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:41.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前もって用意した\N特殊賽を使うと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから それは同じサイコロを…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought they were the same—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロ賽を使うとは\N一言も言ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I never said we were using the 4-5-6 dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:51.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\N特殊賽を仲間うちで回す
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:50.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just that each of us would share our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Share!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:16:00.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No! This is bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:16:01.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメ！通るか そんなメチャクチャ\N無法だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいや\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:02.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:06.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の言うとおりだ\Nお前は認めとったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:07.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You agreed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特殊賽を使うことも\N仲間うちで回すことも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:11.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,About the special dice, and about the sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだそうだ！\N観念しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:15.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大体 てめえは散々\N汚ねえことやっておいて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:17.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're the one who was playing dirty to begin with, why do you care about the rules now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:18.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今さら何が無法だ！\N恥を知れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:18.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Learn some shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sit back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,座れよ\N座れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:23.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sit down! Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:24.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,座れ！座れ！座れ！…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:28.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji had waited for this mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:28.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジが欲しかったのは この空気
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It is why he egged Ohtsuki on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周りが一丸となって\N大槻を責め立てる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:35.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Establish the narrative, and turn the audience to his side!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:35.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理を通し心情的に\N周りを味方につける
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:39.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Without it, he could never corner Ohtsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:40.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでなければ\N大槻を追い詰めることはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ　遠慮なく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:54.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピンゾロ　ピンゾロ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Snake eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Snake eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Snake eyes!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:57.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピンゾロ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Snake! Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:01.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピンゾロ！ピンゾロ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,SNAKE EYES!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Six snake eyes in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:04.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６連続ピンゾロ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたち４５組の張り\N50万7000が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:07.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and the others had bet 507,000 perica,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:12.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その５倍 253万5000に\N膨れ上がる！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:12.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but this becomes 2,535,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:17.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to go fetch your safe to pay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:16.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつを払うには\N持ってくるしかねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:19.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金庫\Nき…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:24.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The box you've been keeping the perica you were saving up in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:24.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前がゴッソリ貯め込んだ\Nペリカの詰まった千両箱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:26.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつを持ってきてもらおうか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:40.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He really was stashing it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:40.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとだったんだな\N貯め込んでるって噂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:45.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんぐらいあんだ？\N1000万　いや2000万か？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wonder how much he's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:45.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ten million? Twenty million?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:48.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの野郎 汚ねえ奴だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:48.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What a scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:52.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目標の2000万\Nあとちょっとだったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:52.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I almost made it to twenty million...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:57.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,253万5000だな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:57.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There it is. 2,535,000 perica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:59.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお！\Nすげえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:06.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえ… すげえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待てよ\Nああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:16.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこに行く？\Nどこって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今夜はもう休ませてもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:22.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've had enough for tonight. Isawa and Numakawa can run things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:23.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとの仕切りは石和と沼川がやる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:26.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Keep going if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:26.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆の衆で勝手にやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:30.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう　やめるんだ？\N一度負けたくらいで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:28.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Quitting already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You only lost once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:34.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？カ… カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:36.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kaiji, isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうこれ以上 いじめんでくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:40.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 気持ちは\N分からないこともない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:40.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't say I don't understand where you're coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:44.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも親は\Nやり切ってもらわないとな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But you need to finish your turn as dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…\N忘れたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:47.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:53.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dealers go twice. You're only off the hook if you roll a 1, something worse, or a pisser.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:53.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親は２回　１回で終われるのは\N１の目以下かションベンの時だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:55.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And your first roll was a 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたの１回目は\N４だったじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sit the fuck down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:03.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,座れよ　もう一度\Nあんたの親で続行だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're dealing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:03.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:12.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張らせてもらう　もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're betting against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全額
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:21.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Together, their bets came to 3,042,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:21.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,積み上げられたのは\N総額304万2000
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And of course, the rules haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無論 ルールはさっきと同じ\N特殊サイを使う
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Special dice are in play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead with yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:33.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠慮なく使ってくれ\Nなっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll be using ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:37.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちも使わせてもらうんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:39.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,似たようなものを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:39.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fair's fair, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:46.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,304万2000\Nこの金が５倍づけとなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:44.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,3,042,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:48.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he pays five times, over 15 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:50.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1500万以上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そ… そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことよ これ！\Nさっきの再現だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:57.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:00.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長の支出はざっと1800万だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:00.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The foreman's gonna be paying out 18 million tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:05.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえ！\Nブッ飛ぶぞ 奴の金庫の金全部！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:05.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's every penny he has!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji has cornered Ohtsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:13.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　ついに大槻を追い詰めた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:16.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At the edge of the abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:16.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄の淵へと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:37.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally in chinchiro, once you roll, everyone's focused on the bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:43.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But during your first roll... You were looking straight into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:48.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Trying to see if I knew you were cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:53.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't been looking at me like that, I'd have made a grab.
